WEBVTT

00:00.120 --> 00:01.125
<i>Back in the '90s,</i>

00:01.166 --> 00:03.492
<i>there was no other
TV phenomenon like "Friends."</i>

00:03.581 --> 00:05.249
<i>Everybody wished they knew them,</i>

00:05.250 --> 00:07.156
<i>or in some cases, wanted to</i> be <i> them.</i>

00:07.234 --> 00:08.709
How <i> you</i> doin'?

00:08.710 --> 00:10.143
Can you <i> be </i> any more like Joey?

00:10.213 --> 00:12.079
Joey only says that to girls.

00:12.080 --> 00:14.419
I don't... I don't know any girls.

00:14.420 --> 00:15.959
<i>The faculty was equally as riveted</i>

00:15.960 --> 00:17.274
<i>watching these "Friends,"</i>

00:17.299 --> 00:18.820
<i>who always had each other's backs.</i>

00:18.845 --> 00:21.109
Barry and I watched the whole
episode together on the phone.

00:21.134 --> 00:22.469
Bonkers that's still happening.

00:22.494 --> 00:24.227
All the choices
along the course of your life,

00:24.282 --> 00:25.781
to end up back at Goldberg.

00:25.813 --> 00:27.249
He may live 500 miles away

00:27.289 --> 00:28.898
studying to become a fancy radiologist,

00:28.952 --> 00:30.417
but I've never felt
more connected to him.

00:30.496 --> 00:31.831
Everything I see reminds me of him.

00:31.887 --> 00:33.386
Like, Coop's grapes
remind me of the time

00:33.455 --> 00:34.754
I fed him on a picnic this summer.

00:34.823 --> 00:36.423
I've seen what that boy does to fruit.

00:36.491 --> 00:37.490
It's disgusting.

00:38.627 --> 00:40.927
- Uh, you gonna get that?
- I can't reach under the fridge.

00:40.996 --> 00:42.695
- Yeah, but it's gonna rot down there.
- Who cares?

00:42.764 --> 00:44.130
God, Coop, stop being such a Monica.

00:44.232 --> 00:45.265
Boy Monica's got a point.

00:45.333 --> 00:46.833
You leave that grape under there,

00:46.902 --> 00:48.468
it's gonna ferment and create wine,

00:48.537 --> 00:49.769
intoxicating the mice.

00:49.838 --> 00:51.971
Can't have drunk mice
running around here.

00:52.848 --> 00:54.381
I will simply lift this fridge

00:54.476 --> 00:56.042
and you come and grab the grape.

00:56.144 --> 00:57.777
Okay.

00:57.802 --> 00:58.822
One...

00:58.847 --> 01:00.146
Ow!

01:00.215 --> 01:02.148
My back!

01:02.217 --> 01:03.417
Damn it, mice! You win again!

